{{vgname|孤岛惊魂：原始杀戮|en=Far Cry Primal|cn=孤岛惊魂：原始杀戮|tw=極地戰嚎：野蠻紀源|official-cn=孤岛-{}-惊魂：野蛮纪源}}是一款由[[育碧蒙特利尔|育碧蒙特利尔]]开发，[[育碧软件|育碧软件]]发行的[[动作冒险游戏|动作冒险游戏]]。游戏于2016年2月23日在[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]平台发行，2016年3月1日在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]平台发行。游戏背景设定在[[石器时代|石器时代]]，讲述了一名猎人塔卡从手无寸铁到成为部落首领的故事。本作也是该系列首次得到官方中文化的作品，游戏包含简体中文和繁体中文版本<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamersky.com/news/201510/675755.shtml|title=育碧确认《孤岛惊魂：原始杀戮》简体中文版同步上市|publisher=[[游民星空|游民星空]]|date=2015-10-23|accessdate=2015-10-24|language=zh-cn|archive-date=2015-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151025140346/http://www.gamersky.com/news/201510/675755.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 游戏玩法 ==

《孤岛惊魂：原始杀戮》是一款[[动作冒险游戏|动作冒险游戏]]。背景设定在虚构大陆Oros，一个充满着[[猛犸象|猛犸象]]、[[恐狼|恐狼]]、[[洞熊|洞熊]]、[[披毛犀|披毛犀]]和[[剑齿虎|剑齿虎]]等野生动物的[[开放世界|开放世界]]。由于游戏设定在史前时代，传统的枪战和车辆等玩法在本作中被移除<ref name="GRadar1" />，玩家只能使用诸如矛、棍棒、斧和短程武器弓等作近距离作战<ref name="GI" />。玩家不能购买武器，必须使用从世界各地搜集的木材和石头來制作。随着玩家的逐渐成长，他们还可使用各种资源来制作更具杀伤性的武器。玩家还須觅食和学习生火<ref name="GSPot" />。除了面对天敌外，玩家也有机会成为部落首领，并带领其他人远离危险。成为部落首领后，玩家須管理和保护他的部落成员<ref name="tribe management" />。游戏还设有昼夜系统<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/far-cry-primal-officially-unveiled-coming-in-early-2016/|title=Far Cry Primal officially unveiled, coming in early 2016|first=Andy|last=Chalk|work=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|date=2015-10-07|accessdate=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151008002842/http://www.pcgamer.com/far-cry-primal-officially-unveiled-coming-in-early-2016/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。到了晚上，一些敌人会变得更具侵略性。玩家可利用火作为工具保护自身安全和进行狩猎<ref name="GI" /><ref name="GSPot">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/far-cry-primal-trailer-release-date-gameplay-detai/1100-6431181/?ftag=MKT5490f8a|title=Far Cry Primal Trailer, Release Date, Gameplay Details Officially Released|first=Tamoor|last=Hussain|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date=2015-10-06|accessdate=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151014195831/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/far-cry-primal-trailer-release-date-gameplay-detai/1100-6431181/?ftag=MKT5490f8a|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 剧情 ==

=== 设定 ===
游戏设定在公元前1万年的[[石器时代|石器时代]]，那时人类刚发现火，并开始用石头制造工具。在一个部落与其他部落及大自然接触并发生冲突的过程中，生存就是最大的挑战<ref name="IGN">{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/10/06/far-cry-primal-announced-with-2016-release-date?|title=''Far Cry Primal'' Announced With 2016 Release Date|first=Mitch|last=Dyer|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=2015-10-07|accessdate=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006202542/http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/10/06/far-cry-primal-announced-with-2016-release-date|dead-url=no}}</ref>。玩家将扮演一个名为塔卡（Takkar）的猎人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/far-cry-primal-lead-character-voiced-by-adam-jense/1100-6431205/|title=''Far Cry Primal'' Lead Character Voiced by Adam Jensen Actor|first=Eddie|last=Makuch|work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date=2015-10-06|accessdate=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007204611/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/far-cry-primal-lead-character-voiced-by-adam-jense/1100-6431205/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在他的狩猎队被伏击后，他被困在了一个曾被冰雪覆盖的蛮荒之地Oros<ref name="GI">{{cite web|url=http://www.gameinformer.com/games/far_cry_primal/b/xboxone/archive/2015/10/06/far-cry-creators-take-the-series-back-to-the-stone-age.aspx?|title=''Far Cry''{{'}}s Creators Take The Series Back To The Stone Age|first=Jeff|last=Cork|work=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]|date=2015-10-06|accessdate=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007203947/http://www.gameinformer.com/games/far_cry_primal/b/xboxone/archive/2015/10/06/far-cry-creators-take-the-series-back-to-the-stone-age.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。最终Takkar会成长为部落族长，领导部落<ref name="tribe management">{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2015/10/6/9454671/far-cry-primal-release-date-announcement-livestream-youtube|title=''Far Cry Primal'' revealed for 2016 release, watch the first trailer here|first=Allegra|last=Frank|work=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]]|date=2015-10-06|accessdate=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007061140/http://www.polygon.com/2015/10/6/9454671/far-cry-primal-release-date-announcement-livestream-youtube|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

