== 开发 ==
游戏由[[育碧蒙特利尔|育碧蒙特利尔]]开发，[[育碧多伦多|育碧多伦多]]、[[育碧乌克兰|育碧基辅]]和[[育碧上海|育碧上海]]负责协助<ref name="IGN" />。2015年1月5日，育碧公布的一项调查，询问玩家他们最喜欢的游戏设定。包括诸如吸血鬼、僵尸、恐龙、后启示录世界、历史战争和类似[[秘鲁|秘鲁]]和[[阿拉斯加|阿拉斯加]]的现代社会等主题<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-01-05-ubisoft-polls-public-on-future-far-cry-settings|title=Ubisoft polls public on future Far Cry settings|first=Tom|last=Phillips|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|date=2015-01-05|accessdate=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007095932/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-01-05-ubisoft-polls-public-on-future-far-cry-settings|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/ubisoft-poll-hints-at-future-far-cry-settings/|title=Ubisoft poll hints at future Far Cry settings|first=Phil|last=Savage|work=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]|date=2015-01-05|accessdate=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007032349/http://www.pcgamer.com/ubisoft-poll-hints-at-future-far-cry-settings/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月6日，育碧通过Twitch暗示了其新作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.destructoid.com/ubisoft-has-a-mystery-stream-going-to-tease-its-next-project-313993.phtml|title=Ubisoft has a mystery stream going to tease its next project|first=Brett|last=Makedonski137|work=[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]|date=2015-10-06|accessdate=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007003221/http://www.destructoid.com/ubisoft-has-a-mystery-stream-going-to-tease-its-next-project-313993.phtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一天后，[[IGN|IGN]]土耳其泄露了游戏。几小时后，官方正式公布了本作的预告<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2015/10/06/far-cry-5-primal-setting/|title=Far Cry Primal Trailer: Fight Mammoths With Spears|first=Alec|last=Meer|work=[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]]|date=2015-10-06|accessdate=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151006235756/http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2015/10/06/far-cry-5-primal-setting/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏的创意总监是让·克里斯托夫·盖约特（Jean-Christophe Guyot），曾开发育碧的[[波斯王子系列|波斯王子系列]]<ref name="GRadar1">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesradar.com/far-cry-primal-stone-age/?tag=grsocial-20|title=Far Cry Primal ditches guns for prehistoric arms|first=Ludwig|last=Kietzmann|work=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]|date=2015-10-07|accessdate=2015-10-07|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007032054/http://www.gamesradar.com/far-cry-primal-stone-age/?tag=grsocial-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏于2016年2月23日登陆[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]平台，2016年3月登陆[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]平台<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.videogamer.com/ps4/far_cry_primal/news/far_cry_primal_sends_the_series_to_the_stone_age_in_february_2016.html|title=Far Cry Primal sends the series to the Stone Age in February 2016|first=David|last=Scammell|date=2015-10-06|accessdate=2015-10-07|work=[[VideoGamer.com|VideoGamer.com]]|archive-date=2015-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151007040435/http://www.videogamer.com/ps4/far_cry_primal/news/far_cry_primal_sends_the_series_to_the_stone_age_in_february_2016.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

